description: Ra Uru Hu's Human Design gate keywords, centers, and channel associations

knowledge.name: The Creative
knowledge.description: Creation as a primal force. The energy potential to manifest inspiration without limitation.

knowledge.name: The Receptive
knowledge.description: Receptivity as the primal base through which any response is determined. The root of action.
knowledge.channelKeynote: The design of being the keeper of keys

knowledge.name: Difficulty at the Beginning
knowledge.description: The fundamental challenge of initiation is to transcend confusion and establish order.

knowledge.name: Youthful Folly
knowledge.description: The energy to beguile and succeed despite ignorance. Freedom from retribution.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of mental ease mixed with doubt

knowledge.name: Waiting
knowledge.description: The fundamental attunement to natural rhythms. Waiting as an active state of awareness.
knowledge.channelKeynote: The design of being in the flow

knowledge.name: Conflict
knowledge.description: The fundamental design component of progress. The law that growth cannot exist without friction.

knowledge.name: The Army
knowledge.description: The point of convergence. By design, the need for leadership to guide and order society.
knowledge.channelKeynote: For 'good' or 'bad' the design of leadership

knowledge.name: Holding Together
knowledge.description: The basic worth realized in contributing individual efforts to group goals.

knowledge.name: The Taming Power of the Small
knowledge.description: Potential can be fulfilled through detailed attention to all pertinent aspects.

knowledge.name: Treading
knowledge.description: The underlying code of behaviour which ensures successful interaction despite circumstances.

knowledge.name: Peace
knowledge.description: A harmonic condition in the individual or society that permits assessment before renewed action.

knowledge.name: Standstill
knowledge.description: The quality of restraint and the importance of meditation and inaction in confronting temptation.
knowledge.channelKeynote: The design of the social being

knowledge.name: Fellowship
knowledge.description: Universal ideas and values in an ordered framework which inspires humanistic cooperation.

knowledge.name: Possession in Great Measure
knowledge.description: The accumulation and retention of power through skilled interaction, coupling grace with control.
knowledge.channelKeynote: The design of being the keeper of keys

knowledge.name: Modesty
knowledge.description: The quality of behaviour which expresses the proper balance between extremes.
knowledge.channelKeynote: The design of being in the flow

knowledge.name: Enthusiasm
knowledge.description: The great art of enriching life by the harmonic channelling of energy.

knowledge.name: Following
knowledge.description: The ancient law that those who wish to rule must know how to serve.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of an organizational being

knowledge.name: Work on What Has Been Spoilt
knowledge.description: The vigilance and determination to uphold and defend basic and fundamental human rights.

knowledge.name: Approach
knowledge.description: That all things are interrelated is apparent and manifested through the action of approach.

knowledge.name: Contemplation
knowledge.description: Recognition and awareness in the now which transforms understanding into right action.

knowledge.name: Biting Through
knowledge.description: The justified and necessary use of power in overcoming deliberate and persistent interference.

knowledge.name: Grace
knowledge.description: A quality of behaviour best suited in handling mundane and trivial situations.
knowledge.channelKeynote: The design of the social being

knowledge.name: Splitting Apart
knowledge.description: Amorality. The awareness and understanding which leads to the acceptance of diversity.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of individuality (Genius to Freak)

knowledge.name: Return
knowledge.description: The natural and spontaneous process of transformation and renewal.

knowledge.name: Innocence
knowledge.description: The perfection of action through uncontrived and spontaneous nature.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of needing to be first

knowledge.name: The Taming Power of the Great
knowledge.description: The maximization of the power of memory applied to the nurturing of continuity.

knowledge.name: Nourishment
knowledge.description: The enhancement of the quality and the substance of all activities through caring.

knowledge.name: Preponderance of the Great
knowledge.description: The transitoriness of power and influence.

knowledge.name: The Abysmal
knowledge.description: The deep within the deep. Persistence despite difficulties has its inevitable rewards.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of succeeding where others fail

knowledge.name: Clinging Fire
knowledge.description: Freedom recognized as an illusion and limitation accepted as a fate.

knowledge.name: Influence
knowledge.description: The law of friction, whether active or passive, that engenders transference and thus influence.
knowledge.channelKeynote: For 'good' or 'bad', the design of leadership

knowledge.name: Duration
knowledge.description: The only thing which endures is change.

knowledge.name: Retreat
knowledge.description: Active withdrawal and the transformation of a weak position into a strength.

knowledge.name: Great Power
knowledge.description: Power is only great when its display or use serves the common good.

knowledge.name: Progress
knowledge.description: By design, progress cannot exist in a vacuum and is dependent on interaction.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of a 'Jack of all Trades'

knowledge.name: Darkening of the Light
knowledge.description: The rule of cycles in which decline is a natural but not enduring stage.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of a 'Jack of all Trades'

knowledge.name: The Family
knowledge.description: The manifestation macro- and micro-cosmically of the organic nature of communities.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of being a part seeking a whole

knowledge.name: Opposition
knowledge.description: The ability to preserve individual integrity through opposition to detrimental forces.

knowledge.name: Obstruction
knowledge.description: The value of obstruction in provoking analysis, assessment and reevaluation.

knowledge.name: Deliverance
knowledge.description: The point of transition between struggle and liberation.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of being a part seeking a whole

knowledge.name: Decrease
knowledge.description: The limitation of resources which maximizes development of potential.

knowledge.name: Increase
knowledge.description: The expansion of the resources which maximizes the development of full potential.

knowledge.name: Breakthrough
knowledge.description: In order for achievement to be maintained a new order must be fairly established.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of individuality (Genius to Freak)

knowledge.name: Coming to Meet
knowledge.description: The success of any interaction is based on the absence of any preconditions.
knowledge.harmonicGateName: The Taming Power of the Great

knowledge.name: Gathering Together
knowledge.description: The natural and generally beneficial attraction of like forces.

knowledge.name: Pushing Upward
knowledge.description: Good fortune that may be perceived as the result of serendipity but derives from effort and dedication.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of succeeding where others fail

knowledge.name: Oppression
knowledge.description: A restrictive and adverse state as a result of internal weakness or external strength or both.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of mental activity and clarity

knowledge.name: The Well
knowledge.description: The necessary and qualitative foundation that is a prerequisite to establish the common good.

knowledge.name: Revolution
knowledge.description: Ideally the transformation of forms based on the highest principles and not simply for power.

knowledge.name: The Cauldron
knowledge.description: The value of historical continuity whose traditional values serve and enrich the present and the future.

knowledge.name: The Arousing
knowledge.description: The ability to respond to disorder and shock through recognition and adaptation.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of needing to be first

knowledge.name: Keeping Still
knowledge.description: Temporary and self-imposed inaction for the benefit of assessment.

knowledge.name: Development
knowledge.description: Development as a structured progression that is both steadfast and enduring.

knowledge.name: The Marrying Maiden
knowledge.description: Interaction in its mundane social context but also one's mystical and cosmic relationships.

knowledge.name: Abundance
knowledge.description: Abundance is strictly a question of spirit.

knowledge.name: The Wanderer
knowledge.description: Stability through movement. The perpetuation of continuity through the linking of short term activity.

knowledge.name: The Gentle
knowledge.description: The extraordinary power of clarity.

knowledge.name: The Joyous
knowledge.description: Stimulation is the key to joy.
knowledge.harmonicGateName: Work on What Has Been Spoilt

knowledge.name: Dispersion
knowledge.description: The ability to break down barriers to achieve union.

knowledge.name: Limitation
knowledge.description: The acceptance of limitation is the first step in transcendence.

knowledge.name: Inner Truth
knowledge.description: The awareness of universal underlying principles.

knowledge.name: Small Preponderance
knowledge.description: Caution, patience and detail produce excellence out of limitation.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of an organizational being

knowledge.name: After Completion
knowledge.description: In the spiral of life, all ends are beginnings.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of mental ease mixed with doubt

knowledge.name: Before Completion
knowledge.description: Transition, like birth, requires a determined strength for the passage through.
knowledge.channelKeynote: A design of mental activity and clarity
